on=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09618\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09618-HK</a>)</td><td>139.30</td><td>-2.45</td></tr><tr><td>百度(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09888:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09888\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09888-HK</a>)</td><td>137.80</td><td>-1.01</td></tr><tr><td>攜程(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09961:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09961\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09961-HK</a>)</td><td>573.50</td><td>-2.05</td></tr><tr><td>阿里(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)</td><td>184.00</td><td>+0.49</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
